          Release Notes:


          It&#039;s about time, the duo consisting of Nag and
          Desecrator launch their debut album. Almost 50
          minutes of cold, grim Black Metal with various
          Thrash and Death Metal influences. Inspired and
          performed by Norwegian Black Metal Elite.
          Outburst of COLD SATANIC DEATH!

          Masterpiece of True Norwegian Black Metal. 9
          Anti-Human and Anti-Life Anthems of total
          desecration. Features Nag (Tsjuder) and Desecrator
          (Endezzma, ex-Tsjuder, ex-Furze). Recorded, mixed
          and mastered at Tripple T Studio with Harald
          Vaernor behind the desk.

          Limited edition of 1.000 copies in a digipack with
          20 pages booklet. The digipack comes with a
          different cover and layout than the regular CD.
